divs: Sighting DetailsI went out to get the cat and take it in for the night. I follow MUFON daily and because of my interest, I glanced up to the sky just in time to see a very high star like object head south at a very rapid pace. Much quicker than a satellite. As I watched, it disappeared as if someone turned off it's light.
